<item>
 <title>On Japan</title>
 <link>http://www.srichinmoycentre.org/node/16074</link>
 <description>
    &lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;front_lotus.jpg&quot; class=&quot;left&quot; src=&quot;http://aum.vasudevaserver.netdna-cdn.com/cdn/farfuture/MJ5iWaUfLsS9eG5MB4GT6rrLbVngYllcAMjCU6YvYf0/mtime:1427741905/files/Members/patanga/front_lotus.jpg&quot; style=&quot;width:125px; height:119px&quot; /&gt;While running through some of the main wards of Tokyo metropolis, I got some poetic inspiration.&amp;nbsp; Just returning from Japan, I got inspired to write something on the plane.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Thank you Guru, thank you Japan.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;My favourites are the last ones, about &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.tokyomeditation.com&quot;&gt;Tokyo&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr /&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;
	&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;
	Japan (I)&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In a land of beauty&lt;br /&gt;
	Sprouts from the earth&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A body of purity and&lt;br /&gt;
	A temple of silence&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Scattering moonlight&lt;br /&gt;
	In starclad firmament&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;
	&lt;br /&gt;
	Sakura sakura&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The life and dynamism&lt;br /&gt;
	And people of elegance&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Skies of silence-vast&lt;br /&gt;
	And Tokyo&amp;rsquo;s might&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;All bow to the minute merry&lt;br /&gt;
	Of Japan&amp;rsquo;s blossomed cherry&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;
	Kamakura&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In Kamakura the flower&lt;br /&gt;
	Turns into silence and power&lt;br /&gt;
	At Lord Buddha&amp;rsquo;s Foot&lt;br /&gt;
	Under his Compassion-Look&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;
	Japan (II)&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Her people the earnest&lt;br /&gt;
	Her life the simplest&lt;br /&gt;
	Her Kyoto the deepest&lt;br /&gt;
	Her Tokyo the greatest&lt;br /&gt;
	&amp;ndash; All march with no rest&lt;br /&gt;
	To fulfil the Supreme&amp;rsquo;s Quest.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;
	Tokyo (I)&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Asia&amp;rsquo;s cherry and&lt;br /&gt;
	Europe&amp;rsquo;s rose &amp;ndash;&lt;br /&gt;
	In the selfsame tree&lt;br /&gt;
	Blossoms Japan&amp;rsquo;s soul.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;
	&lt;br /&gt;
	Tokyo (II)&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Citadel of silence&lt;br /&gt;
	Dreams of the highest&lt;br /&gt;
	In her answered query&lt;br /&gt;
	Japan&amp;rsquo;s five-petaled cherry.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;
	Tokyo (III)&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Her body a land of duty&lt;br /&gt;
	A sky of serenity&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Her vital a fort of purity&lt;br /&gt;
	Blossoming beauty&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Her mind an ocean of silence&lt;br /&gt;
	In vastness peace&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Her heart an altar of simplicity&lt;br /&gt;
	In the house of infinity&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In all of them flourishes&lt;br /&gt;
	Japan&amp;rsquo;s jewel Tokyo &amp;ndash;&lt;br /&gt;
	The joint streak&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Of a smile from the Sun&lt;br /&gt;
	And a tear from the Moon.&lt;/p&gt;


    

    &lt;img src=&quot;http://aum.vasudevaserver.netdna-cdn.com/cdn/farfuture/Qm3lNJhp7aIJZsFkKUwSWJNVNrZvrTqxSTuD6av2qr0/mtime:1427741935/files/featured-images/patanga/frontlotus.jpg&quot; width=&quot;125&quot; height=&quot;119&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; /&gt;    

    &lt;div class=&quot;addressfield-container-inline locality-block country-BR&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;locality&quot; x-autocompletetype=&quot;locality&quot; autocomplete=&quot;locality&quot;&gt;Tokyo&lt;/span&gt; -  &lt;span class=&quot;state&quot; x-autocompletetype=&quot;region&quot; autocomplete=&quot;region&quot;&gt;--&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;country&quot; x-autocompletetype=&quot;country&quot; autocomplete=&quot;country&quot;&gt;Brazil&lt;/span&gt;    

    &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.srichinmoycentre.org/category/interests/writing&quot;&gt;Writing &amp;amp; Poetry&lt;/a&gt;    

    Article (to appear in member/country blogs)    

    Poems on Japan, inspired by a long run through Tokyo    

    POINT (-90.3556715 36.2339133)    

