<item>
 <title>The Hero-Warrior - Aphorisms by Sri Chinmoy</title>
 <link>http://www.srichinmoycentre.org/node/13897</link>
 <description>
    &lt;p&gt;Translated to Portuguese by Patanga Cordeiro.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Source: &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.srichinmoylibrary.com&quot;&gt;www.srichinmoylibrary.com&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
	&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
		Be a hero-warrior&lt;br /&gt;
		Who always fights&lt;br /&gt;
		For truth and justice-light.&lt;br /&gt;
		&lt;br /&gt;
		Seja um her&amp;oacute;i-guerreiro&lt;br /&gt;
		Que sempre luta&lt;br /&gt;
		Pela verdade e justi&amp;ccedil;a-luz.&lt;/p&gt;
	&lt;p&gt;- Sri Chinmoy&lt;/p&gt;
	&lt;hr /&gt;
	&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
		&lt;br /&gt;
		God expects&lt;br /&gt;
		Every human heart&lt;br /&gt;
		&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; To be&lt;br /&gt;
		A God-hero-warrior.&lt;br /&gt;
		&lt;br /&gt;
		Deus espera&lt;br /&gt;
		Que cada cora&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o humano&lt;br /&gt;
		&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; Seja&lt;br /&gt;
		Um her&amp;oacute;i-guerreiro-Deus.&lt;br /&gt;
		&lt;br /&gt;
		- Sri Chinmoy&lt;/p&gt;
	&lt;hr /&gt;
	&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
		The battle of life&lt;br /&gt;
		Is for the hero-warrior&lt;br /&gt;
		&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; Supreme.&lt;br /&gt;
		&lt;br /&gt;
		A batalha da vida&lt;br /&gt;
		&amp;Eacute; para o her&amp;oacute;i-guerreiro&lt;br /&gt;
		&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; Supremo.&lt;br /&gt;
		&lt;br /&gt;
		- Sri Chinmoy&lt;/p&gt;
	&lt;hr /&gt;
	&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
		&lt;br /&gt;
		God&amp;rsquo;s Victory-Chariot beckons&lt;br /&gt;
		Only those who want to be&lt;br /&gt;
		&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; Hero-warriors.&lt;br /&gt;
		&lt;br /&gt;
		A Carruagem-Vit&amp;oacute;ria de Deus chama&lt;br /&gt;
		Apenas aqueles que desejam ser&lt;br /&gt;
		&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; Her&amp;oacute;is-guerreiros.&lt;br /&gt;
		&lt;br /&gt;
		- Sri Chinmoy&lt;/p&gt;
	&lt;hr /&gt;
	&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
		&lt;br /&gt;
		If you want&lt;br /&gt;
		To be awakened inwardly,&lt;br /&gt;
		Then God will eventually&lt;br /&gt;
		Turn you into a hero-warrior.&lt;br /&gt;
		&lt;br /&gt;
		&lt;br /&gt;
		Se voc&amp;ecirc; quer estar&lt;br /&gt;
		Ser interiormente desperto,&lt;br /&gt;
		Deus por fim lhe transformar&amp;aacute;&lt;br /&gt;
		Num her&amp;oacute;i-guerreiro.&lt;br /&gt;
		&lt;br /&gt;
		- Sri Chinmoy&lt;/p&gt;
	&lt;hr /&gt;
	&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
		HERE and NOW&lt;br /&gt;
		I must inspire&lt;br /&gt;
		The hero-warrior-souls&lt;br /&gt;
		On earth&lt;br /&gt;
		Not to retire.&lt;br /&gt;
		&lt;br /&gt;
		AQUI e AGORA&lt;br /&gt;
		Devo inspirar&lt;br /&gt;
		As almas-her&amp;oacute;is-guerreiras&lt;br /&gt;
		Na Terra&lt;br /&gt;
		Para que nunca desistam.&lt;br /&gt;
		&lt;br /&gt;
		- Sri Chinmoy&lt;/p&gt;
	&lt;hr /&gt;
	&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
		A saint is a seeker&lt;br /&gt;
		Who endlessly continued.&lt;br /&gt;
		&lt;br /&gt;
		O santo &amp;eacute; um buscador&lt;br /&gt;
		Que continuou at&amp;eacute; o fim.&lt;br /&gt;
		&lt;br /&gt;
		- Sri Chinmoy&lt;/p&gt;
	&lt;hr /&gt;
	&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;See &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.meditacaosp.com/articles/o-heroi-guerreiro/&quot;&gt;more poems on the Hero-Warrior&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;


    

